(362, 12, 'section_01_blocks_0_caption', '<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-512\" src=\"http://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/‘au2019-level-h2-chemistry-weekly-classes-300x228.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"228\" />Our weekly progressive tuition classes are catered for Sec 3-5 &amp; JC1/2. Get ready and be inspired by Dr. Aw and Miss Tham with their unique IM-POSSIBLE Chemistry learning strategies that will ensure you see improvement in your concept and the ability to solve questions.'),
