(366, 12, 'section_01_blocks_1_caption', '<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-513\" src=\"http://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/‘au2019-level-‘ou2019-chemistry-crash-courses-300x228.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"228\" />We conduct frequent FREE Booster class series based on the topic student find most difficulty . This will be a good revision for students who wish to recap/refresh the key concept learnt as well the FAQ exam types of questions.'),
