(370, 12, 'section_01_blocks_2_caption', '<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-515\" src=\"http://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/‘ipu2019-‘ou2019-level-chemistry-weekly-classes-300x228.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"228\" />A systematic and thorough review of the all frequently tested topic in exam will be reviewed during the June intensive lessons. The lesson is conducted with incremental difficulty level and broken down into 3 steps: Concept explanation, Demonstration by tutor and Student repeat with increasing difficulty.'),
