(8346, 414, 'google_reviews_3_description', 'Before entering JC, I was warned by many that A level Chemistry was going to be tough. That was when my sister recommended me to you. I’m a very logical person, things has to clear to me like, How can this tuition help me achieve my A in Chemistry? What resources can the teachers provided, which are superior to those given in school? You made me realise that chemistry was not as challenging and inaccessible as I initially thought to be. You were patient and knowledgeable, able to give precise explanation any clarity any doubts. Your notes and teachings were really easy to understand and learn.\r\n\r\nThank you for building the perfect foundation for my Chemistry. Thank you for helping me get an A for chemistry which is nothing short of a miracle! All I needed is a little effort on my part and the A was mine. I will want you as your Chemistry tutor, because really, you are really an awesome teacher. Not only because of how capable you are, but because you truly have a heart for your students. I wouldn’t have conquered survived Chemistry without your help. Joining Uptas became easily one of the best decisions I have ever made in my life. In just one lesson, I could understand the concepts, link topics together and remember things. Chemistry was made more interesting with the detailed explanations!'),
