(10729, 546, 'banner_bottom_cards_0_caption', '<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-502 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-05-at-3.03.59-PM-300x228.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"228\" />\r\n\r\nTutors have a very good track record (with more than 12 years of teaching experience) and with percentage of distinctions more than 95.1% for O\' / IP Level and 91.8% for GCE A\'Level. Co-Founder Dr. AW has been awarded with many prestigious awards notably: ASTAR Scholar, NTU Nanyang President Scholarship and featured in \"The Straights Times\" for Superior Teaching Methodology.'),
