(11418, 607, '_tour_cards', 'field_63be47bcea614'),
(11419, 607, 'element_3_title', 'Formative Assessment Close Monitoring of Students'),
(11420, 607, '_element_3_title', 'field_63be48588efb1'),
(11421, 607, 'element_3_caption', 'As an award winning tutor, Dr Aw constantly check on the understanding of students. Dr Aw uses effective questioning techniques and provides feedback by marking the students work.'),
(11422, 607, '_element_3_caption', 'field_63be4893ce3cd'),
(11423, 607, 'element_3_image', '600'),
(11424, 607, '_element_3_image', 'field_63be48e7da366'),
(11425, 607, 'element_4_title', 'Booster Class (FOC) For students to catch up earlier chapters'),
(11426, 607, '_element_4_title', 'field_63be486c8efb2'),
(11427, 607, 'element_4_caption', 'Booster class is a special revision class that we have created which will be held once per week catered for all existing students to catch up earlier contents or misconception that they may have missed. The best part is the class is FOC (Free of Charge) for all existing students.'),
(11428, 607, '_element_4_caption', 'field_63be48a7ce3ce'),
(11429, 607, 'element_4_image', '601'),
(11430, 607, '_element_4_image', 'field_63be4900da367'),
(11431, 607, 'element_5_title', 'Chemistry can be interesting!'),
(11432, 607, '_element_5_title', 'field_63be48768efb3'),
(11433, 607, 'element_5_caption', 'Everyone knows how difficult to memorise facts and formulae from lecture books. At Uptas Learning, students are shown the wonders of Chemistry and begin their journey of further discovery. Students will be able visualize chemistry in real life and science coming alive.'),
(11434, 607, '_element_5_caption', 'field_63be48b5ce3cf'),
(11435, 607, 'element_5_image', '603'),
(11436, 607, '_element_5_image', 'field_63be491bda368'),
(11437, 607, 'element_6_title', 'Mastery Skill Level Practices'),
(11438, 607, '_element_6_title', 'field_63be487e8efb4'),
(11439, 607, 'element_6_caption', 'We understand every students have different needs and so we created 3 different levels of problem solving questions namely: Skill Level 1, 2 and 3. Skill level 1 are easy-medium difficult types of questions for students to polish their basic, skill level 2 will be focusing on higher order thinking questions (Medium-Difficult questions) and skill level 3 (Oh, My God! Level). This level is catered for students who wants the most difficult types of questions.'),
(11440, 607, '_element_6_caption', 'field_63be48bcce3d0'),
(11441, 607, 'element_6_image', '604'),
(11442, 607, '_element_6_image', 'field_63be492bda369'),
(11443, 607, 'element_7_title', 'Harnessing on Technology to Enhance Learning Experience'),
(11444, 607, '_element_7_title', 'field_63be48868efb5'),
(11445, 607, 'element_7_caption', 'By leveraging on computer simulations and videos, Dr Aw is able to bring across challenging topics in a better visualised manner. In this manner, the key concept is better understood and what used to take 30 mins or more to understand in school, we are confident to simplified and explain in just a couple of minutes with deeper understanding.\r\n\r\nDr Aw replaced whiteboard markers with his Ipad. This allows a smooth flow of presentations and dynamically changes colour and highlight key concepts to students.\r\n\r\nAnd we also using virtual lab environment to simulate experimental procedures where students are able to visualize and capture the essence of what is required to do well in their practical examinations.'),
(11446, 607, '_element_7_caption', 'field_63be48c4ce3d1'),
(11447, 607, 'element_7_image', '605'),
(11448, 607, '_element_7_image', 'field_63be493bda36a'),
(11449, 607, 'element_7_image_2', '606'),
(11450, 607, '_element_7_image_2', 'field_63be4951da36b'),
(11451, 607, 'tour_posts', ''),
(11452, 607, '_tour_posts', 'field_63be49b802d86'),
(11453, 607, 'tour_cards_0_title', 'Topic: Chemical Bonding'),
(11454, 607, '_tour_cards_0_title', 'field_63be47d1ea615'),
(11455, 607, 'tour_cards_0_caption', 'Every chapter are sorted to concept levels. Through many years of interactions with students, we have discovered that the secret to doing well in exam lies in getting the key concept of the chapter correct.\r\n\r\nAn analogy will be if focuses are doors, then key concept will be the keys to the doors where students will see the big picture of the content. In this manner, we will further break down each focus point to concept keys where misconception will be clarified and the door to distinctions will be opened.'),
(11456, 607, '_tour_cards_0_caption', 'field_63be47dfea616'),
(11457, 607, 'tour_cards_0_image', '594'),
(11458, 607, '_tour_cards_0_image', 'field_63be47efea617'),
(11459, 607, 'tour_cards_1_title', 'Student Attention Span'),
(11460, 607, '_tour_cards_1_title', 'field_63be47d1ea615'),
(11461, 607, 'tour_cards_1_caption', 'In Uptas Learning Hub, we recognise that students attention span is short and follows a general trend as indicated in graph 1. Therefore, the lessons are planned carefully where there will be regular changes in the activities of the class so as to interrupt the process of losing their attention (Graph 2). In this way, this will help students focus better and absorb more in class.'),
(11462, 607, '_tour_cards_1_caption', 'field_63be47dfea616'),
(11463, 607, 'tour_cards_1_image', '596'),
(11464, 607, '_tour_cards_1_image', 'field_63be47efea617'),
(11465, 607, 'tour_cards_2_title', 'Top Quality Notes'),
(11466, 607, '_tour_cards_2_title', 'field_63be47d1ea615'),
(11467, 607, 'tour_cards_2_caption', 'When Dr Aw created the worksheet, he will trial the questions in the shoes of students. In doing so, he is able to anticipate the conceptual challenges faced by the students.'),
(11468, 607, '_tour_cards_2_caption', 'field_63be47dfea616'),
(11469, 607, 'tour_cards_2_image', '597'),
(11470, 607, '_tour_cards_2_image', 'field_63be47efea617'),
