(323, 1, '2022-12-09 09:14:35', '2022-12-09 09:14:35', '<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>East (BEDOK): Block 209, New Upper Changi Road #03-647 Singapore 460209. It is just a 3 minutes sheltered walk from Bedok MRT, just above Sheng Siong Supermart.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Central (BISHAN): 1 Sin Ming Rd, B2-09 Thomson V Two, B2, Unit 4, Singapore 575629. MRT Near by: Marymount: (7 -10 mins walk) &amp; Thomson East Coast Line: (3-5 mins walk)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Where are you located?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-title-one', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:41:24', '2023-01-05 06:41:24', '', 0, 'http://uptas.test/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=323', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(324, 1, '2022-12-09 09:14:47', '2022-12-09 09:14:47', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We accept walk in or call in sales enquiries (Whatsapp: 91705114) and online registration. However, most of our students are recommended through word of mouth from relatives and friends. Seats are often limited and once the capacity is full, we will stop accepting new students.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How to Contact Us?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-title-two', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:43:45', '2023-01-05 06:43:45', '', 0, 'http://uptas.test/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=324', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(325, 1, '2022-12-09 09:14:58', '2022-12-09 09:14:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://Uptas.sg/Trial\">Online Reservation</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interested to join us? You may make a reservation via the link below or you can also call us @+6591705114</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How do I register for the classes?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-title-three', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:44:54', '2023-01-05 06:44:54', '', 0, 'http://uptas.test/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=325', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(326, 1, '2022-12-09 09:15:09', '2022-12-09 09:15:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When our class reach to a size of about 15, we will open new classes to reduce the average size of the class. As we allow students to perform make up classes, therefore we cannot commit to a class size but generally the weekend class is bigger than the weekday classes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We can ensure the quality of each lesson will not be compromised regardless of the class size and where the students are from. Our tutors are so well versed in the subject that they know exactly where the misconception are often located and able to accurately anticipate the questions the student will ask. Our tutors will also know what are the questions the students will ask but did not ask.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How big is the class size?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-title-four', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:50:29', '2023-01-05 06:50:29', '', 0, 'http://uptas.test/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=326', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(327, 1, '2022-12-09 09:15:21', '2022-12-09 09:15:21', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We achieve an average of more than 95.1% &amp; 91.8% distinction every year for GCE O\' level and A\' Level Respectively</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How did the students perform every year for O\' & A\' level?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-title-five', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:48:20', '2023-01-05 06:48:20', '', 0, 'http://uptas.test/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=327', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(328, 1, '2022-12-09 09:15:32', '2022-12-09 09:15:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are numerous students complained to use that their teachers do not know how to delivery the teachings well and the lecture notes lacked details. However, there are also others who complained the notes being too detailed and difficult to comprehend. This may make learning difficult and students find it overwhelming to even solve a simple question.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our task here is to ensure we find the best tutor and getting just the right amount of simplified content and sufficient practices ranging from basic, intermediate to advanced level to be delivered to the student.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The lesson is basically broken up into 3 parts: Absorb, Apply and Acknowledge</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A:&nbsp;<strong>Absorb</strong>&nbsp;the concept</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A:&nbsp;<strong>Apply</strong>&nbsp;the knowledge</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A: <strong>Acknowledge</strong> and learn from your mistakes. <strong>Do not repeat them.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'What is your teaching methodology and how it is different from other tuition center or MOE schools?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-title-six', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:49:13', '2023-01-05 06:49:13', '', 0, 'http://uptas.test/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=328', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
