(486, 1, '2023-01-05 06:51:43', '2023-01-05 06:51:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Regardless of the time that you join the class, we will ensure you will be able to catch up with the rest of the class and preparing you in the coming examination. However, you have to know that the class is not going to slow down for you and you will be positively stressed to run alongside with them and from our experience, you will learn faster under this environment. In order to ensure you are always on the right track, we will provide you with the essential notes and practice exercises for you to master the topics and with tutors helping to answer all your queries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Will I be able to catch up as I join late?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'will-i-be-able-to-catch-up-as-i-join-late', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:51:44', '2023-01-05 06:51:44', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=486', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(487, 1, '2023-01-05 06:52:34', '2023-01-05 06:52:34', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have a very limited vacancy in the class. The trial class is come on a first come first serve basis. Once, the vacancy is up, there will be no trial class available. To sign up for a trial class, please visit this <a href=\"http://uptas.sg/trial\">link</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Is there a trial lesson?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'is-there-a-trial-lesson', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:52:34', '2023-01-05 06:52:34', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=487', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(488, 1, '2023-01-05 06:53:10', '2023-01-05 06:53:10', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The goal of Uptas Learning Hub is that you can learn from the best teacher in the market at an affordable rate which is co-shared by the rest of your classmates. We do not advocate a 1-1 private tuition center as it will mean at least 10 times higher for the same time slot, learning the same concept within the same group session.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Do you provide 1-1 private tuition?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'do-you-provide-1-1-private-tuition', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:53:10', '2023-01-05 06:53:10', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=488', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(489, 1, '2023-01-05 06:53:38', '2023-01-05 06:53:38', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The lessons in the Uptas Learning Hub will cater for both IP and non-IP student as the student are very similar. However, one of the key difference in the question for the IP stream is the questions are more difficult. We have a huge data base that will cater your needs and able to do customized notes with practices to help you accelerate your learning and with sufficient amount of practices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Do you provide IP tuition?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'do-you-provide-ip-tuition', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:53:39', '2023-01-05 06:53:39', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=489', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(490, 1, '2023-01-05 06:54:26', '2023-01-05 06:54:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The payment is by per term (defined as 10 ~ 12 lessons)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Is the payment monthly or termly?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'is-the-payment-monthly-or-termly', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:54:26', '2023-01-05 06:54:26', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=490', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(491, 1, '2023-01-05 06:55:06', '2023-01-05 06:55:06', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We accept only cheque, paynow, paylah and internet bank transfer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'What is the accepted form of payment?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-is-the-accepted-form-of-payment', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:55:07', '2023-01-05 06:55:07', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=491', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(492, 1, '2023-01-05 06:55:27', '2023-01-05 06:55:27', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, you certainly can ask questions after class.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Can I clarify my doubts or some queries I may have in school after class?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-i-clarify-my-doubts-or-some-queries-i-may-have-in-school-after-class', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:55:28', '2023-01-05 06:55:28', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=492', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
(493, 1, '2023-01-05 06:56:13', '2023-01-05 06:56:13', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can whatsapp @+6591705114. Our friendly tutors and administrators will be happy to answer any queries regarding our classes. Alternatively, you can also fill up our online form (under our contact us page) and we will contact you as soon as possible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How can I contact the agency to find out more / register?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-can-i-contact-the-agency-to-find-out-more-register', '', '', '2023-01-05 06:56:14', '2023-01-05 06:56:14', '', 0, 'https://www.ongoing.website/websites/uptas/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=493', 0, 'faqs', '', 0),
